Symbol.Script_3D:
! ========= Grab Bar.gsm =========
if iDetlevel3D = DETLEVEL3D_OFF then end if iDetlevel3D = DETLEVEL3D_SIMPLE then gs_resol = 6
if not(gs_shadow) then shadow off
! ========= Hotspots =========
hotspot half_a, 0, 0, 204, inc_angle, 4+128 hotspot (length/2)*cos (inc_angle), 0, -length/2*sin (inc_angle), 2, inc_angle, 5 ! right end hotspot 0, 0, 0, 206, inc_angle, 6 hotspot 0, b, 0, 207, inc_angle, 7
roty inc_angle
hotspot 0, 0, 0, 101, b, 1+256 ! middle point hotspot 0, -b, 0, 1, b, 2 hotspot 0, 2*b, 0, 103, b, 3
hotspot 0, 0, 0, 301, half_length, 1+128, length hotspot -half_length, 0, 0, 3, half_length, 2, length ! left end hotspot length, 0, 0, 303, half_length, 3, length
if length > 3*ror then hotspot -length/2+ror, 0, 0, 401, b, 1+128 ! left elbow hotspot -length/2+ror, -b, 0, 4, b, 2 hotspot -length/2+ror, b, 0, 403, b, 3
hotspot length/2-ror, 0, 0, 501, b, 1+128 ! right elbow hotspot length/2-ror, -b, 0, 5, b, 2 hotspot length/2-ror, b, 0, 503, b, 3 endif
unID = 1000
! ========= Tube =========
material tube_mat pen gs_cont_pen
put -length/2, 1, 0, 1, -length/2, 0, 0, 1, -length/2, ror-b, 0, 1
for i = 1 to gs_resol/2 alpha = i*90/(gs_resol/2) put -length/2+ror-ror*cos (alpha), -b+ror-ror*sin (alpha), 0, 1 next i
put length/2-ror, -b, 0, 1
for l = 1 to gs_resol/2 alpha = l*90/(gs_resol/2) put length/2-ror+ror*sin (alpha), -b+ror-ror*cos (alpha), 0, 1 next l
put length/2, 0, 0, 1, length/2, 1, 0, 1
addy -0.005 cutplane -90 del 1
tube 2, (NSP/4), 16+32,
0, 0, 900, di/2, 360, 4001,
get(NSP)
cutend
! ========= Elbows =========
add -length/2, ror-b, 0 rotx -90
addz b-ror-0.005 resol 1.5*gs_resol prism_ 2,0.005, 0, 0, 979, di/2+0.01, 360, 4079
add length, 0, 0 resol 1.5*gs_resol prism_ 2,0.005, 0, 0, 979, di/2+0.01, 360, 4079
Symbol.Script_2D:
! ========= Grab Bar.gsm =========
! ========= Hotspots ========== if a > 3*ror then hotspot2 0, 0, 101, b, 1+256 hotspot2 0, -b, 1, b, 2+128 hotspot2 0, 2*b, 103, b, 3 else hotspot2 0, 0, 101, b, 1+256 hotspot2 0, -b, 1, b, 2 hotspot2 0, 2*b, 103, b, 3 endif
hotspot2 0, 0, 301, half_a, 1+128, a hotspot2 -length* cos (inc_angle)/2, 0, 3, half_a, 2, a ! left overhang hotspot2 a, 0, 303, half_a, 3, a
hotspot2 0, 0, 201, half_a, 1+128, a hotspot2 length* cos (inc_angle)/2, 0, 2, half_a, 2, a ! right overhang hotspot2 -a, 0, 203, half_a, 3, a
if a > 3*ror then hotspot2 cos (inc_angle)* (length/2-ror), -b, 401, b, 2 hotspot2 cos (inc_angle)* (length/2-ror), 0, 4, b, 1+128 hotspot2 cos (inc_angle)* (length/2-ror), b, 403, b, 3
hotspot2 -cos (inc_angle)* (length/2-ror), -b, 501, b, 2 hotspot2 -cos (inc_angle)* (length/2-ror), 0, 5, b, 1+128 hotspot2 -cos (inc_angle)* (length/2-ror), b, 503, b, 3 endif
unID = 1000
pen gs_cont_pen fill gs_fill_type
if inc_angle <= 15 then ! ========= Elbows ========== poly2_B 5, 7, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, -a/2-di/2-0.01, 0, 1, -a/2-di/2-0.01, -0.005, 1, -a/2+di/2+0.01, -0.005, 1, -a/2+di/2+0.01, 0, 1, -a/2-di/2-0.01, 0, 1
poly2_B 5, 7, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, a/2-di/2-0.01, 0, 1, a/2-di/2-0.01, -0.005, 1, a/2+di/2+0.01, -0.005, 1, a/2+di/2+0.01, 0, 1, a/2-di/2-0.01, 0, 1
! ========= Railing ========= if b-ror < 0 then poly2_B 11, 7, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, -a/2+ror, -b+di/2, 1, -a/2+ror, -b+ror, 901, 0, -90+asn ((ror-b+0.005)/(ror-di/2)), 4001, -a/2+ror- (ror-b+0.005) /tan (asn ((ror-b+0.005)/(ror+di/2))), -0.005, 1, 0, 90- asn ((ror-b+0.005)/(ror+di/2)), 4001, a/2-ror, -b-di/2, 1, a/2-ror, -b+ror, 901, 0, 90-asn ((ror-b+0.005)/(ror+di/2)), 4001, a/2-ror+(ror-b+0.005) /tan (asn ((ror-b+0.005)/(ror-di/2))), -0.005, 1, 0, -90+ asn ((ror-b+0.005)/(ror-di/2)), 4001, -a/2+ror, -b+di/2, 1 else poly2_B 16, 7, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, -a/2-di/2, -0.005, 1, -a/2-di/2, -b+ror, 1, -a/2+ror, -b+ror, 901, -a/2+ror, -b-di/2, 3001, a/2-ror, -b-di/2, 1, a/2-ror, -b+ror, 901, a/2+di/2, -b+ror, 3001, a/2+di/2, -0.005, 1, a/2-di/2, -0.005, 1, a/2-di/2, -b+ror, 1, a/2-ror, -b+di/2, 3001, -a/2+ror, -b+di/2, 1, -a/2+ror, -b+ror, 901, -a/2+di/2, -b+ror, 3001, -a/2+di/2, -0.005, 1, -a/2-di/2, -0.005, 1 endif else PROJECT2{2} 3, 270, 3+32+1024, gs_fill_pen endif
Symbol.Script_VL:
call "FM_types_BA_WMCC" parameters all
VALUES "a" RANGE (ror,) values "half_a" range [ror/2, ) VALUES "b" RANGE [0.04,) VALUES "di" RANGE [0.01,) VALUES "ror" RANGE [2*di,)
values{2} "iDetlevel3D" DETLEVEL3D_DETAILED, typRes[1], DETLEVEL3D_SIMPLE, typRes[2], DETLEVEL3D_OFF, typRes[3]
VALUES "gs_resol" RANGE [3,) VALUES "inc_angle" RANGE [0,90] VALUES "length" RANGE [2*ror,) values "half_length" range [ror,)
IF gs_cont_pen=0 THEN PARAMETERS gs_cont_pen=7 IF gs_fill_pen=0 THEN PARAMETERS gs_fill_pen=91
IF iDetlevel3D = DETLEVEL3D_SIMPLE THEN HIDEPARAMETER "gs_resol" IF iDetlevel3D = DETLEVEL3D_OFF THEN HIDEPARAMETER "gs_resol", "gs_shadow"
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "A" or GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "half_a" then if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "half_a" then A = 2 * half_a parameters A = A else half_a = A/2 parameters half_a = half_a endif
zzyzx = A*tan (inc_angle) length = A/cos (inc_angle) half_length = A/cos (inc_angle)/2 parameters zzyzx = zzyzx, length = length, half_length = half_length else if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "ZZYZX" then a = zzyzx/ tan (inc_angle) length = zzyzx/ sin (inc_angle) half_length = (zzyzx/ sin (inc_angle))/2 parameters a = a, length = length, half_length = half_length else if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "half_length" then length = 2 * half_length parameters length = length else half_length = length/2 parameters half_length = half_length endif
a = length* cos (inc_angle) zzyzx = length* sin (inc_angle) parameters a = a, zzyzx = zzyzx endif
half_a = A/2 parameters half_a = half_a endif
